             was indicted for <rs id="t18220220-194-off1045" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220220-194-off1045" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-194-off1045" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220220-194-cd1046" type="crimeDate">6th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-194-off1045 t18220220-194-cd1046"></join>, three sovereigns, three crowns pieces, three half-crowns, and one shilling
            </rs>, the monies of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220220-194-victim1752" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Adams
                  <interp inst="t18220220-194-victim1752" type="surname" value="Adams"></interp>
